function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
    --Play voctory music stinger and wait to reset music
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Boss_Astaroth_Victory")
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ID_ARENA_ENTRANCE_DONAN, 0.5)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idDonan)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(gizmoGate,false)

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	idAstarothLoc = idActorKilled
	ptDonan = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idDonan)
	ptDonanRunTo = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idAstarothLoc)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards
	idFirstTimeRewardLocation = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(sFirstTimeRewardDropActor, idAstarothMountCorpse)
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drorp occurs
		-- idFirstTimeRewardLocation is set/created on "Actor Killed)
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idFirstTimeRewardLocation, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Astaroth", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Astaroth")
	end
	
	-- Since this boss doesn't have its own treasure class, also drop generic treasure at this time
	Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idFirstTimeRewardLocation, "Campaign_Boss")
	
	-- Remove the Reward Actor
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFirstTimeRewardLocation)
	------------------------------------------------------
			
end

function Start()

	tCurrentPlayer = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	--Reset Music
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent")
	
	--Enable mourning Donan and Yorin's corpse
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idYorin)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idAstarothMountCorpse)
	
	--Inject Donan's Conversation List
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_FIGHT_COMPLETE_01, tCurrentPlayer[1])
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	-- Set guards outside gate to use normal anims
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_M_GUARD_01)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_M_GUARD_01, "NPC_Idle")
	Hydra.ActorSetConversationStatus(ID_M_GUARD_01, true)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.3)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_F_GUARD)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_F_GUARD, "NPC_Idle")
	Hydra.Wait(0.6)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_M_GUARD_02)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_M_GUARD_02, "NPC_Idle")

end

--Play Boss Music Phase 2
Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Boss_Astaroth_Phase2")
end
